OL,3,CCeltic boss Rodgers 'saddened' by
OL,4,C'good girl' remark reaction
OL,6,FCeltic boss Brendan Rodgers has said
OL,7,Fhe "had a laugh" about the sexism row
OL,8,Fover his "good girl" comment with the
OL,9,Fjournalist involved.
OL,11,FRodgers said he was "saddened" by the
OL,12,Freaction, while the BBC Scotland
OL,13,Fsports reporter he made the comment
OL,14,Fto, Jane Lewis, has said she believes
OL,15,Fhe did not mean to offend and she has
OL,16,Fnot taken any offence.
