OL,6,FDuring a BBC Sportsound radio
OL,7,Finterview following Celtic's 3-1 win
OL,8,Fagainst Motherwell on Sunday, the
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland man was heard saying
OL,10,F"good girl" following a line of
OL,11,Fquestioning from Ms Lewis.
OL,13,FThe Celtic manager told a press
OL,14,Fconference at Celtic Park on Tuesday:
OL,15,F"I have spoken to Jane. She wasn't
OL,16,Foffended.
