OL,3,CCeltic boss Rodgers 'saddened' by
OL,4,C'good girl' remark reaction
OL,6,F"We had a laugh about it, she will
OL,7,Fcontinue to ask me awkward questions,
OL,8,FI'm sure. But I see her every week and
OL,9,Fwe have good relations, like I have
OL,10,Fwith most people in my life, whether
OL,11,Fthat's professional or social.
OL,13,F"Sadly for me, in society now, we are
OL,14,Feither looking to offend or find
OL,15,Fsomething that is offensive to try and
OL,16,Fpin on to people.
