OL,3,CCeltic boss Rodgers 'saddened' by
OL,4,C'good girl' remark reaction
OL,6,F"I find it saddening as much as
OL,7,Fanything because one, I am not that
OL,8,Ftype of person, I can never be that,
OL,9,Fit's not how I'm built. But also it
OL,10,Fsaddened me for society now because
OL,11,Fpeople are just trying to find ways to
OL,12,Fsomehow bring you down if they can.
OL,13,FIt's not nice."
OL,15,FMs Lewis said on Tuesday: "Clearly,
OL,16,Fthe interview on Sunday has become a
OL,17,Ftalking point. I don't believe there
OL,18,Fwas any offence meant by Brendan
OL,19,FRodgers ` and for my part, there was
OL,20,Fnone taken."
