OL,6,FHe replied: "No, no, you know exactly
OL,7,Fwhat I mean," but the journalist then
OL,8,Fsaid: "I'm actually not sure exactly
OL,9,Fwhat you mean."
OL,11,FHe then appeared to wrap up the
OL,12,Finterview by saying: "Done, good girl,
OL,13,Fwell done."
OL,15,FA spokeswoman for the Scottish
OL,16,FFeminist Network said: "Rodgers's
OL,17,Fthrowaway comment encourages other
OL,18,Ffootball fans to behave in a similar
OL,19,Fway, demeaning women they work with or
OL,20,Fengage with.
