OL,6,F"It has to stop.
OL,8,F"Jane Lewis was just doing her job,
OL,9,Ftrying to extract an explanation from
OL,10,FBrendan Rodgers on his cryptic comment.
OL,12,F"That the go-to attitude of a manager
OL,13,Fof a winning team was condescension is
OL,14,Fquite illuminating but really very
OL,15,Fdepressing in 2024. We thought
OL,16,Fdinosaurs were extinct."
OL,18,FA spokeswoman at For Women Scotland
OL,19,Fsaid: "It's depressing that casual
OL,20,Fsexism is still embedded in sport.
